    <title>sass入门（一）</title>
    <link href="https://levehlw.github.io/blog/2021/06/09/scss%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>https://levehlw.github.io/blog/2021/06/09/scss%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89/</id>
    <published>2021-06-09T11:46:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-06-10T03:41:31.033Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、sass安装"><a href="#一、sass安装" class="headerlink" title="一、sass安装"></a>一、sass安装</h2><p>sass需要安装ruby，先从<a href="http://www.ruby-lang.org/zh_cn/downloads/">官网下载安装</a>ruby，安装时需要勾选<code>Add Ruby executables to your PATH</code>添加到系统环境变量。</p><p>安装完成后，使用下面命令测试是否安装成功：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ruby -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装成功后切换国内源：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gem update --system // 更新gem到最新版本</span><br><span class="line">// 删除并替换原有源</span><br><span class="line">gem sources --add https://gems.ruby-china.com/ --remove https://rubygems.org/</span><br><span class="line">gem sources -l</span><br><span class="line">// 确保只有https://gems.ruby-china.com </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用gem安装compass和sass：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gem install sass</span><br><span class="line">gem install compass</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><h2 id="二、sass编译"><a href="#二、sass编译" class="headerlink" title="二、sass编译"></a>二、sass编译</h2><p>使用以下命令行可以将sass编译为css文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//单文件转换命令</span><br><span class="line">sass input.scss output.css</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//单文件监听命令</span><br><span class="line">sass --watch input.scss:output.css</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//如果你有很多的sass文件的目录，你也可以告诉sass监听整个目录：</span><br><span class="line">sass --watch app/sass:public/stylesheets</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="koala编译工具"><a href="#koala编译工具" class="headerlink" title="koala编译工具"></a>koala编译工具</h3><p>koala是一款免费的sass编译器，<a href="http://koala-app.com/">下载地址</a>。</p><h2 id="Live-Sass"><a href="#Live-Sass" class="headerlink" title="Live Sass"></a>Live Sass</h2><p>live-sass为vscode扩展，能够实时将sass文件转换为css。</p><h3 id="sumline扩展sass-build编译器"><a href="#sumline扩展sass-build编译器" class="headerlink" title="sumline扩展sass-build编译器"></a>sumline扩展sass-build编译器</h3><p>需要先安装package control后才能安装使用，在搜索sass-build安装，tools-&gt;build system-&gt;sass。ctrl+B编译scss文件。</p><h2 id="二、sass基本类型、变量定义"><a href="#二、sass基本类型、变量定义" class="headerlink" title="二、sass基本类型、变量定义"></a>二、sass基本类型、变量定义</h2><p>sass支持6种数据类型：</p><ol><li>数字，<code>1, 2, 13, 10px</code></li><li>字符串，有引号字符串与无引号字符串，<code>&quot;foo&quot;, &#39;bar&#39;, baz</code></li><li>颜色，<code>blue, #04a3f9, rgba(255,0,0,0.5)</code></li><li>布尔型，<code>true, false</code></li><li>空值，<code>null</code></li><li>数组 (list)，用空格或逗号作分隔符，<code>1.5em 1em 0 2em, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif</code></li><li>maps, 相当于 JavaScript 的 object，<code>(key1: value1, key2: value2)</code></li></ol><h3 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h3><p>变量以$符号开头，示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$width</span>:<span class="number">100px</span>; <span class="comment">// :类似c语言中的=号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="数组的用法"><a href="#数组的用法" class="headerlink" title="数组的用法"></a>数组的用法</h3><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$list</span>:(<span class="number">100px</span>,<span class="number">200px</span>)</span><br><span class="line">//使用</span><br><span class="line">width:nth(<span class="variable">$list</span>,<span class="number">1</span>); <span class="comment">//数组下标从1开始</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">100px</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="map的用法"><a href="#map的用法" class="headerlink" title="map的用法"></a>map的用法</h3><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$map</span>: (top: <span class="number">1px</span>;<span class="attribute">left</span>:<span class="number">2px</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 用法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">padding-left</span>: map-get(<span class="variable">$map</span>, left);</span><br><span class="line">----</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">padding-left</span>: <span class="number">2px</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用@each函数遍历：</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.div</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">@each</span> <span class="variable">$key</span>, <span class="variable">$value</span> in <span class="variable">$map</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        #&#123;<span class="variable">$key</span>&#125;:<span class="variable">$value</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">---------------</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.div</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">top</span>: <span class="number">1px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">left</span>: <span class="number">2px</span>; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="sass的加减乘除基本运算"><a href="#sass的加减乘除基本运算" class="headerlink" title="sass的加减乘除基本运算"></a>sass的加减乘除基本运算</h2><h3 id="数值运算"><a href="#数值运算" class="headerlink" title="数值运算"></a>数值运算</h3><p>数值加、减可以数值直接相加减，数值的乘法则不能同时为长度值。</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">10px + 10px <span class="comment">// 20px</span></span><br><span class="line">10px + 10 <span class="comment">// 20px</span></span><br><span class="line">10px - 10px <span class="comment">// 0px</span></span><br><span class="line">10px - 10 <span class="comment">// 0px</span></span><br><span class="line">10px * 10px <span class="comment">//报错</span></span><br><span class="line">10px * 10 <span class="comment">//100px</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>/符号在css中用于分割数字值，同时它在sass中也被赋予了除法运算符的含义，在某些情况下会被识别为除法运算符。</p><ol><li>如果值，或值的一部分，是变量或者函数的返回值。（表达式中存在变量或者有函数返回值）</li><li>如果值被圆括号包裹</li><li>如果值是算数表达式的一部分</li></ol><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font</span>: <span class="number">10px</span>/<span class="number">8px</span>;             <span class="comment">// 普通css</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable">$width</span>: <span class="number">1000px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="variable">$width</span>/<span class="number">2</span>;            <span class="comment">// Uses a variable, does division</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">width</span>: round(<span class="number">1.5</span>)/<span class="number">2</span>;        <span class="comment">// Uses a function, does division</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">height</span>: (<span class="number">500px</span>/<span class="number">2</span>);          <span class="comment">// Uses parentheses, does division</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-left</span>: <span class="number">5px</span> + <span class="number">8px</span>/<span class="number">2px</span>; <span class="comment">// Uses +, does division</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="颜色值运算"><a href="#颜色值运算" class="headerlink" title="颜色值运算"></a>颜色值运算</h3><p>颜色值的运算是分段进行，也就是说先计算出RGB三部分的值，然后在编译为颜色值。</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#010203</span> + <span class="number">#040506</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>计算 <code>01 + 04 = 05</code> <code>02 + 05 = 07</code> <code>03 + 06 = 09</code>，然后编译为</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#050709</span>; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="字符串运算"><a href="#字符串运算" class="headerlink" title="字符串运算"></a>字符串运算</h3><p><code>+</code> 可用于连接字符串</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">cursor</span>: e + -resize;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译为</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">cursor</span>: e-resize; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;一、sass安装&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#一、sass安装&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;一、sass安装&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;一、sass安装&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;sass需要安装ruby，先从&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ruby-lang.org/zh_cn/downloads/&quot;&gt;官网下载安装&lt;/a&gt;ruby，安装时需要勾选&lt;code&gt;Add Ruby executables to your PATH&lt;/code&gt;添加到系统环境变量。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;安装完成后，使用下面命令测试是否安装成功：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ruby -v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;安装成功后切换国内源：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;gem update --system // 更新gem到最新版本&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;// 删除并替换原有源&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;gem sources --add https://gems.ruby-china.com/ --remove https://rubygems.org/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;gem sources -l&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;// 确保只有https://gems.ruby-china.com &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;使用gem安装compass和sass：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;gem install sass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;gem install compass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
